    <item>
      <title>周二缅因州和南卡罗来纳州初选的要点</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/10/us/politics/maine-platner-primary-senate-election-results.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格雷厄姆·普拉特纳赢得了缅因州参议院民主党初选，并迅速将他的民粹主义信息转向共和党现任议员苏珊·柯林斯。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/10/us/politics/maine-platner-primary-senate-election-results.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 07:07:48 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>史蒂夫·希尔顿 (Steve Hilton) 击败汤姆·斯泰尔 (Tom Steyer) 在加州州长竞选中赢得第二名</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/steve-hilton-california-governor-xavier-becerra.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[得到特朗普总统支持的共和党人史蒂夫·希尔顿(Steve Hilton)将在大选中对阵民主党人泽维尔·贝塞拉(Xavier Becerra)。另一位民主党人汤姆·斯泰尔(Tom Steyer)不会晋级。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/steve-hilton-california-governor-xavier-becerra.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 04:49:06 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>内华达州总检察长赢得民主党州长提名</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/nevada-governor-primary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[11 月，亚伦·福特 (Aaron Ford) 轻松击败了瓦肖县 (Washoe County) 专员亚历克西斯·希尔 (Alexis Hill)，获得了与州长乔·隆巴多 (Joe Lombardo) 的接替。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/nevada-governor-primary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 04:44:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>林赛格雷厄姆赢得南卡罗来纳州共和党参议院初选</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/south-carolina-senate-graham-lynch.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[格雷厄姆已连任四届，是在共和党坚定支持的州赢得大选的热门人选。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/south-carolina-senate-graham-lynch.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:46:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>布兰奇曾被视为缓和特朗普的策略。现在他全力以赴。</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/blanche-trump-justice-department-retribution.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[托德·布兰奇的崛起表明，即使在特朗普总统的司法部中，最初也被认为是越界的做法似乎已成为当今的惯例。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/blanche-trump-justice-department-retribution.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:32:10 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>桑德斯支持的加州摇摆区对抗瓦拉达的进步</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/bains-villegas-california-democrats-primary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[兰迪·维勒加斯（Randy Villegas）将面对现任共和党人大卫·瓦拉道（David Valadao），他在竞争激烈的选区经历了无数挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/bains-villegas-california-democrats-primary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 01:02:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>被赫格斯解雇的海军上将晋级决选以取代梅斯</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/nancy-lacore-mace-south-carolina.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[南希·拉科雷 (Nancy Lacore) 将在 2021 年选区面临一场艰难的秋季选举，该选区将更加支持共和党。她正在寻求取代众议员南希·梅斯，后者竞选州长失败，而不是竞选连任。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/nancy-lacore-mace-south-carolina.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:55:42 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>独立议员凯文·凯利 (Kevin Kiley) 将在加州众议院竞选中对阵理查德·潘 (Richard Pan)</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/pan-ho-kiley-california-primary.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[凯利先生今年早些时候放弃了共和党身份。人们普遍认为新划分的第六国会选区对民主党有利。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/pan-ho-kiley-california-primary.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Wed, 10 Jun 2026 00:04:27 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院无视约翰逊并通过民主党主导的劳工法案</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/house-passes-union-contract-bill-bucking-republican-leaders.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[二十名共和党议员与议长迈克·约翰逊决裂，与民主党人一起支持一项修改《国家劳动关系法》的法案。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/house-passes-union-contract-bill-bucking-republican-leaders.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 23:30:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>众议院通过共和党 700 亿美元移民法案</title>
      <link>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/house-immigration-bill.html</link>
      <description><![CDATA[此次投票最终通过了共和党的一项巨额法案，该法案旨在为特朗普总统剩余任期内的移民执法提供资金，从而为他的签署扫清了障碍。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.nytimes.com/2026/06/09/us/politics/house-immigration-bill.html</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 09 Jun 2026 22:11:36 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
